<!-- title -->

    <h3 class="title">
      Pizza SAUCE
    </h3>

<!-- /title -->

<!-- topic post -->

    <p>
    people eat pizza for all different reasons. for me, it's the sauce. i love to order extra sauce. but i would love even more  aplace that didn't require or encourage me to do so. any pizza recommendations based on SAUCE alone?
    </p>

    <p class="author">
    <a href="/topics/show/312667"><img align="absmiddle" src="/images/permalink.gif" alt="link to this post" title="Link to this post"></a> posted by <a href="/users/show/12853">mr mouther</a> on <span class="local-time" title="Thu, 27 Jul 2006 00:00:22 GMT"></span></p>
  
  
    <ul class="post-operators">
    </ul>
  </div> <!-- post-box-content -->

