  <p>
    In central Orange County, try Haus of Pizza. It's a cooked sauce on the sweet side, and garlicky. I don't got there much because I'm generally not fond of thick, bready crusts. But for your request, I wouldn't hesitate to send you there for that sauce on fresh garlic pie w/ sausage.<br/><br/>1500 Adams Ave # 108<br/>Costa Mesa, CA 92626<br/>714-751-8777
  </p>
  
  

